For "Clarke_1866": "Clarke_1866".replace('_19', '') → "Clarke_1866" (no _19), .replace(/[Cc]larke\_18/, 'clrk') → "clrk66" → YES, matches Ellipsoid "clrk66".

For "Custom spheroid": no replacements → "Custom spheroid" → NO, doesn't match any Ellipsoid.

So my approach of checking `match(Ellipsoid, json.ellps)` would work.

